<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SmartMemo verificationCode email</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body
  style="font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; height: 100vh; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background-color: #FFFFFF;">
  <div
    style="max-width: 600px; width: 100%; padding: 40px; background: #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid #FFFFFF; text-align: left; letter-spacing: -1px;">
    <div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
      <img src="cid:logo" alt="SmartMemo 로고" style="height: 20px;">
    </div>
    <h1 style="font-size: 1.6rem; color: #282828; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: -1px;">똑똑한 메모회원가입 인증 번호
    </h1>
    <hr
      style="width: 100px; border: none; border-top: 1.6px solid #CAEBE8; margin: 10px 0 20px 0; margin-bottom: 30px;">
    <div style="font-size: 1rem; color: #282828; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: -1px;">
      <p><strong>
          <%= email %>
        </strong> 님,<br>
        [ 똑똑한 메모 ] 회원가입을 위한 인증 번호를 보내드립니다.<br>
        [ 똑똑한 메모 ] 에서 아래의 인증 번호를 입력해주세요.</p>
    </div>
    <div
      style="display: block; background-color: #3EA99F; color: white; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: bold; width: 200px; height: 60px; line-height: 60px; border-radius: 10px; letter-spacing: 10px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center;">
      <%= authCode %>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #8A8D8A;">*인증 번호는 5분 동안 유효합니다.</p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>